fields.description:
This feature request comes from Christopher Buchino at GotVMail.  He would like to see Crucible integration with Microsoft Visual Studio, similar to our IDE Connector for IntelliJ.

More specifically..
{quote} ..[the web UI] is not very user friendly when it comes to managing the list of files to choose in a review. Additionally, you can't do things like right-click->Go to definition to jump to a method either in the file you are browsing or in another. Being able to use the Visual Studio IDE and add comments directly from there would make our Crucible use much more rewarding.{quote}
